'''Ghosts''' are [[monster]]s which can fought in certain places throughout [[RuneScape Classic]], such as the [[Taverley dungeon]] and [[Draynor Manor]] and [[Wilderness]].

There is also a ghost [[NPC]] during [[The Restless Ghost]] quest.

